# =====================================================
# Reservations (/reservations)
# =====================================================

### Get Reservation By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/2
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Hotel Reservation By ReservationNumber
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/hotel/1280586
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Hotel Reservation By Email and ReservationNumber
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/verify/email@correo.com/1280586
Accept: application/json


### Create Reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
{
  "reservationDate": "2025-12-18",
  "personId": 1,
  "consumptionCenterId": 1,
  "offerId": 1,
  "createdBy": "Rick",
  "paxCount": 4,
  "notes": "Mesa cerca de la ventana",

  "availability": {
    "date": "2025-12-18",
    "startTime": "16:00:00",
    "endTime": "17:00:00",
    "inventoryId": 2
  }
}

### Search Availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/availability
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
{
  "offerId": 1,
  "consumptionCenterId": 1,
  "date": "2025-12-18",
  "paxCount": 4
}

