### Get Consumption Centers By Site
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/consumptioncenter/site/1

### Get Consumption Centers By Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/consumptioncenter/type/1
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}

### Get Consumption Center Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/consumptioncenter/types

### Get Consumption Center Inventory
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/consumptioncenter/inventory/1
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
